UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 1878
1 Section 1. The Transportation Cabinet shall designate the portion of US 460
2 West from mile marker 7.1 to mile marker 8.4 in Menifee County as the "Gary Lee
3 Egelston Memorial Highway" and shall, within 30 days of the effective date of this
4 Resolution, erect appropriate signage denoting this designation.
